	<chapter xml:id="clbv1.17.14">
		<title>v1.17.14, February 26, 2013</title>
		<itemizedlist>
			<title>Resolved Issues</title>
			<listitem>
				<para>When deleting a health monitor of any type, every node on
					that load balancer that is enabled or has failed
					and is in OFFLINE status is now returned to the
					ONLINE status regardless of the health of the
					node.</para>
			</listitem>
			<listitem security="internal">
				<para>Logs are now uploaded to the correct datacenter based on the
					environmental region. This eliminates the billing
					issues for files.</para>
			</listitem>
		</itemizedlist>
		<itemizedlist>
			<title>Resources</title>
